From 45e774b0e0aab786d07930b1b3c12b08bd21d9d1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ykiko <ykiko@clice.io>
Date: Fri, 15 May 2026 23:52:27 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] [Clang][AST] Fix ExplicitInstantiationDecl accessors
 confusing declared type with class encoding

---
 clang/include/clang/AST/DeclTemplate.h        | 38 +++++-----
 clang/lib/AST/DeclTemplate.cpp                | 50 ++++++------
 clang/lib/Sema/SemaTemplate.cpp               |  6 +-
